                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Magelos are nice to add to gear questions, it's really hard to know what to suggest with no info to work with
<br />

<br />
soooo
<br />

<br />
the abbreviated AA speech
<br />

<br />
get your defensive AAs, LT5 and ID 5 at the very least, preferably LR5 ID5, RM5, DI5. If you don't have ER3 get it/ Get ND 3Get SCS3. Keep ROZ on you and your pet, and MAKE the cleric Virt your pet. Also make sure the group gives you all dropped dots. Doppleganger is also a great get out of death free card.
<br />

<br />
Post a magelo for gear suggestions</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Starmist
<br />
<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=520295" target="_blank" class="postlink"><span style="font-weight: bold">magelo profile</span></a>
<br />
Alliance of Hope
<br />
Zebuxorak</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
