                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Mezrin Kortex wrote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">Easiest and quickest upgrade is to max out all languages and get the charm I am wearing.  Great enchanter stats and could probably max all languages in a day if you have a friend that can teach them to you.</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

<br />
You can do it without your friend knowing the language.
<br />

<br />
1)  Make sure your INT is over 255.
<br />
2)  Group with someone (I used my bazaar mule).
<br />
3)  Train level 1 in the language at your guildmaster.
<br />
4)  (Zone to a different zone than the one your group member is in.) &lt;-- I can't recall if this is required, but it is what I did.
<br />
5)  Spam your group with some phrase in the chosen language (I use my /incoming message).
<br />
6)  When maxed, switch language.
<br />

<br />
The OoW charm is nice.  Last time I looked, it went for 10K on my server.  I am elementally flaged, so it doesn't help me, but it does my other characters.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=37024" target="_blank" class="postlink">Serius</a>
<br />
''Dead enchanters take no faction hits''
<br />
Member, Code of Silence
<br />
Luclin Server</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
